B. All records and documents necessary to demonstrate her compliance with the requirements of the Sections 521-527 of the GLB Act, 15 U.S.C. § 6821-6827 inclusive, specifically including, but not limited to, Section 521(g) of the GLB Act, 15 U.S.C. § 6821(g), in the event that Defendant intends to rely upon this exception to the prohibited business practices described in Paragraph I; and

C . Copies of any complaints received by Defendant regarding Defendant’s sale of customer information of a financial institution.

